1 a re port to the Oklahoma Department of Commerce detailing the
2 qualitative effects of at least two projects that received funds
3 pursuant to the Rural Economic Action Plan of 1996.
4 C. Any expenditures associated with creating the plan required
5 by subsection A of this section and the report required by
6 subsection B of this section shall be made using the initial
7 planning expenditure payments authorized pursuant to subsection C of
8 Section 2011 of Title 62 of the Oklahoma Statutes.
9 SECTION 2. This act shall become effective November 1, 2025.
